data.description: Permaculture Off-Grid Farm w/ 88.7 acres + Two Secluded 3 BR/ 2 Bth Homes built in 2015 offering a unique opportunity to embrace sustainable living. Situated the furthest back, 231 SS Rd, a 3 BR/2 bath ranch farmhouse, is completely self-sufficient w/ a 15x40 root cellar, battery bank, & solar field. The bonus room & office provide flexible space for various needs, while the large covered porch makes for a relaxing evening. Additionally, there is an unfinished tiny house that holds great potential as an Airbnb. Water management is effortless thanks to the presence of 3 swales and 3 catchment ponds, which efficiently distribute water to the numerous fruit and vegetable plants scattered across the property. Storage solutions abound including a 30x24 carport & 30x40 workshop. Nature lovers will appreciate the vast natural woods that dominate the landscape, providing excellent hunting opportunities for turkey, deer, quail, & more. Located approx 1 hr from Raleigh, this property offers the ideal balance of tranquility and accessibility. Don't miss this amazing chance to experience Off Grid living on your own homestead!
